HEADWORD: granular
<hw>gran"u*lar</hw> <pr>(gr⟦acr⟧n"⟦usl⟧*l⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[Cf. F. <ets>granulaire</ets>. See <er>Granule</er>.]</ety>
<def>Consisting of, or resembling, grains; <as>as, a <ex>granular</ex>
